{"title":"Saudi construction project of the day","link":"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/~/906504221/0/marginalrevolution~Saudi-construction-project-of-the-day.html","date":1729407206000,"content":"<blockquote>\r\n<p>Saudi Arabia is preparing to begin construction work on its next giga-project: a cube-shaped skyscraper big enough to fit 20 Empire State Buildings.</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/~/t/0/0/marginalrevolution/~https://newmurabba.com/en/the-mukaab/\" target=\"_blank\">The Mukaab</a> will be 400-meters on each side when construction is finished, which would make it the largest built structure in the world. The building will be the centerpiece of New Murabba, a community the country hopes will be a new destination within the capital city of Riyadh.</p>\r\n<p>“It’s masquerading as a building today but it’s so much more,” <a href=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/~/t/0/0/marginalrevolution/~https://newmurabba.com/en/about-us/executive-management/\" target=\"_blank\">Michael Dyke</a>, chief executive officer of New Murabba, said in an interview. “Ultimately, a capital city the size of Riyadh deserves to have a global, central icon as other capital cities do.”</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<p>Here is <a href=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/~/t/0/0/marginalrevolution/~https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-19/saudi-arabia-s-next-giga-project-is-a-gigantic-cube-in-riyadh?sref=htOHjx5Y\" target=\"_blank\">more from Zainab Fattah at Bloomberg</a>.  Here are <a href=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/~/t/0/0/marginalrevolution/~https://www.google.com/search?sca_esv=acead9db038712b1&amp;q=mukaab+riyadh&amp;udm=2&amp;fbs=AEQNm0Aa4sjWe7Rqy32pFwRj0UkWd8nbOJfsBGGB5IQQO6L3J3ppPdoHI1O-XvbXbpNjYYyyK5vBQSXmmfgAtXwDT_UwvibZ0pSIVFX3lVg5uBH9KRkcNkP3cvvJNBG5JuLgxBs03YF7ZheWmRhqfgCmBhS5o6SAZhDu3x8rWio402rJbDrei-2czWxVeRKadRtxLzMWgsQxFmZAWJEMLz75bbUBEJgcKw&amp;sa=X&amp;ved=2ahUKEwjv9rX15pqJAxVRADQIHYM8A7AQtKgLegQICxAB&amp;biw=1280&amp;bih=585&amp;dpr=1.5\" target=\"_blank\">various images based on artist renderings</a>.  Here is <a href=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/~/t/0/0/marginalrevolution/~https://www.google.com/search?sca_esv=acead9db038712b1&amp;q=mukaab+riyadh&amp;source=lnms&amp;fbs=AEQNm0Aa4sjWe7Rqy32pFwRj0UkWd8nbOJfsBGGB5IQQO6L3J3ppPdoHI1O-XvbXbpNjYYyyK5vBQSXmmfgAtXwDT_UwvibZ0pSIVFX3lVg5uBH9KRkcNkP3cvvJNBG5JuLgxBs03YF7ZheWmRhqfgCmBhS5yZO_qSYPUz1kdaqkhrbFz3Mf8Q0E_4snLTQxYAI7iP8mYotlN5aOxhpc520NgyAQJl-AZw&amp;sa=X&amp;ved=2ahUKEwjrwI355pqJAxWyDDQIHUcrBFYQ0pQJegQIEhAB&amp;biw=1280&amp;bih=585&amp;dpr=1.5\" target=\"_blank\">further information</a>.</p>\r\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/~/t/0/0/marginalrevolution/~https://marginalrevolution.com/marginalrevolution/2024/10/saudi-construction-project-of-the-day.html\">Saudi construction project of the day</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/~/t/0/0/marginalrevolution/~https://marginalrevolution.com\">Marginal REVOLUTION</a>.</p>\r\n<img height=\"1\" width=\"1\" src=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/~/i/906504221/0/marginalrevolution\" />\r\n<div><a href=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/_/28/906504221/marginalrevolution\"><img height=\"20\" src=\"https://assets.feedblitz.com/i/fblike20.png\" /></a> <a href=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/_/29/906504221/marginalrevolution,\"><img height=\"20\" src=\"https://assets.feedblitz.com/i/pinterest20.png\" /></a> <a href=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/_/24/906504221/marginalrevolution\"><img height=\"20\" src=\"https://assets.feedblitz.com/i/x.png\" /></a> <a href=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/_/19/906504221/marginalrevolution\"><img height=\"20\" src=\"https://assets.feedblitz.com/i/email20.png\" /></a> <a href=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/_/20/906504221/marginalrevolution\"><img height=\"20\" src=\"https://assets.feedblitz.com/i/rss20.png\" /></a> <a href=\"https://marginalrevolution.com/marginalrevolution/2024/10/saudi-construction-project-of-the-day.html#comments\"><img height=\"20\" src=\"https://assets.fee